 Logging library (from ESP-IDF)

 Path:     firmware/external/esp_log
 Upstream: https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf
           components/log
 License:  Apache License 2.0

 This is a logging library from Espressif's ESP-IDF components, modified as
 necessary for platform porting and project integration purposes.

